ional training at nine.\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 312}, {\"ngram\": \"professional training\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swimming was initially for her an important life skill and good exercise before she started to move up in the swimming groups and entered competitions.\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Swimming\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 373}, {\"ngram\": \"good exercise\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"the swimming groups\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 490}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has now ignited Nepal's medal hopes in the Asian Games and the Olympics .\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 537, \"end\": 542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 0.9999999992442099, \"rank\": 7.558367421251763e-10, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Asian Games\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 575}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 592}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel immensely proud to represent Nepal and I have always tried to give my level best.\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 633, \"end\": 638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 0.9999999992442099, \"rank\": 7.558367421251763e-10, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my level\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think sport plays a big role in creating a community and brings a sense of unity and national pride.\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"spor